# β1 = one unit increase in X changes Y by β1 units

# Log-Linear:
# β1 * 100 = approximate % change in Y

# Linear-Log:
# 1% increase in X changes Y by β1/100 units

# Log-Log:
# β1 = elasticity (% change in X -> % change in Y)

# Logistic:
# exp(β1) = odds ratio

